22
00:01:16,080 --> 00:01:19,240
The most important thing now is to quickly save Yun'er.

23
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:23,320
I'm afraid Feng Chen will find this place soon.

24
00:01:24,240 --> 00:01:27,160
I worry you can't handle him alone.

25
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:27,840
Mother,

26
00:01:28,440 --> 00:01:29,080
