27
00:01:30,520 --> 00:01:31,920
I will protect you all completely.

28
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:36,880
It's best to be cautious in everything.

29
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:48,200
Goods are hated when discarded on the ground, no need to hoard them for oneself.

30
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:53,320
Strength is hated when not exerted from oneself, no need to use it for selfish purposes.

31
00:01:53,600 --> 00:01:56,600
