44
00:02:32,079 --> 00:02:33,120
I remember,

45
00:02:33,480 --> 00:02:37,079
pictographs, ideographs, compound ideographs, and phonetic-semantic compounds.

46
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,079
Yun'er, you're so clever.

47
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,880
But remember,

48
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,800
no matter which method is used,

49
00:02:44,040 --> 00:02:46,000
each character has its own structure.

50
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,520
These alone are not complete enough.

51
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,440
Mother,

52
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,040
there are so many characters.

53
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:11,000
These characters are so small.

54
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:14,720
Heaven is clear, Earth is turbid.

55
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:16,960
Heaven moves, Earth is still.

56
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,760
Yang is clear, Yin is turbid.

57
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,320
Yang moves, Yin is still.

58
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,760
Observe the heart within,

59
00:03:23,760 --> 00:03:25,079
the heart is without a heart.

60
00:03:25,280 --> 00:03:26,600
Observe the form without,

61
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:27,560
the form is without a form.

62
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:29,280
Observe objects from afar,

63
00:03:29,880 --> 00:03:31,200
