The true constant attains its nature.

72
00:03:52,600 --> 00:03:54,360
Always respond, always be still.

73
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:56,800
Such tranquility.

74
00:03:57,760 --> 00:03:59,560
Gradually entering the true way.

75
00:04:00,440 --> 00:04:02,080
To transform all living beings.

76
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,720
This is called attaining the Way.

77
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:07,040
Those who can comprehend it

78
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,800
